snippet.title: Blossoms Bloom Brightest - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Blossoms Bloom Brightest is a sci-fi, yuri visual novel that was originally created as a project for the Yuri Game Jam in 2016.

The game features partial voice acting, featuring Melissa Sternenberg as Erica Matthews, Arietta as Kotoha Ichinose, and Rose Franklin as Sara Evans.

SYNOPSIS:
Three strangers are thrust into an unexpected situation together—they awaken only to find themselves on a spaceship called the Blossom.

A mysterious journey lies ahead of them; what misadventures will they experience over the next two weeks?
